{"word":"H8083 - שְׁמֹנֶה - shᵉmôneh - shem-o-neh' - Eight","slug":"H8083","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שְׁמֹנֶה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shᵉmôneh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shem-o-neh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Eight"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DE;&#x05D5;&#x05E0;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DE;&#x05E0;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DE;&#x05D5;&#x05E0;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DE;&#x05E0;&#x05D4; - sh<sup>e</sup>mo&#x0302;neh  sh<sup>e</sup>mo&#x0302;neh  sh<sup>e</sup>mo&#x0302;na&#x0302;h  sh<sup>e</sup>mo&#x0302;na&#x0302;h</b> - <i>(1,2) shem-o-neh', (3,4) shem-o-naw'</i><p/>Apparently from <a href=\"#/H8082\">H8082</a> through the idea of <i>plumpness</i>; a cardinal number, <i>eight</i> (as if a <i>surplus</i> above the &ldquo;perfect&rdquo; seven); also (as ordinal) <i>eighth: - </i>eight ([-een, -eenth]), eighth."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8066\">H8066</a>, <a href=\"#/H8067\">H8067</a>, <a href=\"#/H8084\">H8084</a>"}]}